*********************ADHITHYAN PORTFOLIO**************************:)
Look and Style
Color Scheme: The website uses a minimalistic color scheme, predominantly featuring white and shades of blue, which gives it a professional and sleek appearance.
Typography: Clean and legible fonts are used throughout, ensuring readability. Headings and subheadings are well-defined, making the content easy to navigate.
Icons and Graphics: The website includes various icons, particularly from FontAwesome, adding to the visual appeal and providing intuitive navigation cues.
Structure and Layout
Header:

Navigation Bar: Includes links to different sections of the site (Home, About, Resume, Portfolio, Services, and Contact). The navigation bar is sticky, staying at the top as you scroll down.
Hero Section: Features a welcoming message with your name and a brief introduction, accompanied by a call-to-action button.
Main Sections:

About Section: Provides a detailed introduction, including a profile picture and a summary of your background, skills, and interests.
Resume Section: Contains a brief overview of your professional experience and education, with a downloadable PDF version of your resume available.
Portfolio Section: Showcases your projects with images and descriptions. Each project can be clicked to view more details.
Services Section: Lists the services you offer, described with icons and brief texts.
Contact Section: Includes a contact form where visitors can send you messages directly. Also features your email address, LinkedIn profile link, and other contact information.
Footer: Contains links to your social media profiles and a copyright notice.

Interactive Features
Smooth Scrolling: Navigating through the different sections is seamless due to smooth scrolling effects.
Hover Effects: Buttons and project images have subtle hover effects, enhancing the user experience.
Loading Progress: Uses Pace.js to show a loading progress bar at the top of the page, improving user perception of loading times.
Technical Details
Responsive Design: The website is fully responsive, adapting well to different screen sizes, from desktops to mobile devices.
Modern Web Practices: Utilizes HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript for a modern, standards-compliant website. Modernizr is used to ensure compatibility across different browsers.
Conclusion
Your portfolio website is well-designed with a professional aesthetic and user-friendly layout. It effectively showcases your skills, experience, and projects, providing visitors with a comprehensive view of your professional profile. The use of modern web technologies ensures that the site is responsive and accessible across various devices and browsers.

# Adhithyan SK - Portfolio

This repository contains the code for my personal portfolio website. It showcases my skills, projects, and professional background. 

## Table of Contents
- [Demo](#demo)
- [Features](#features)
- [Technologies Used](#technologies-used)
- [Installation](#installation)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [Contact](#contact)

## Demo
You can view the portfolio live [here](https://adhiwebs63.netlify.app/).

## Features
- **Responsive Design:** The website is fully responsive and works on all devices.
- **Smooth Scrolling:** Navigate the sections with smooth scrolling effects.
- **Interactive Elements:** Includes interactive elements like progress bars and portfolio modals.
- **Social Media Integration:** Links to my social media profiles.
- **Downloadable Resume:** Option to download my resume directly from the website.

## Technologies Used
- **HTML5:** Markup language used for structuring the content.
- **CSS3:** Styling the HTML elements with custom styles.
- **JavaScript:** Adding interactive features and functionality.
- **Pace.js:** For page load progress bars.
- **Modernizr:** For feature detection to ensure cross-browser compatibility.
- **FontAwesome:** Icons for social media links and other elements.


